name: Sarabi - Thicccbrowz
bio: *hissing noises*! I'm Sarabi - Thicccbrowz. I want to live in a world where people believe that one day cats will rule this planet. I once dreamed of being a Dispensary Clerk. Now I can be found talking about how much I lift all day. Will you be the cinammon to my peanut butter?
